{"tid":632337,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[去火星吧!] 聯想集團 (992) 火箭升空準備區","createTime":"2018-04-17T09:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T08:19:41.000Z","uid":106204,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b050e6683a47599a5e1e27003ec58dd8b0a212a5","tid":632337,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"聯想集團(<a href=\"http://00992.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00992.HK&d=nwxsaOv4DVDwxxgDlY5mHXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=22c2ab88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00992.HK</a>)董事長楊元慶出席聯想誓師大會時表示，在過去一年聯想營業額重拾增長，並達到三年來最高，相信最艱難的日子已經過去，並再一次進入上升的通道。<br />\n<br />\n他指出2018/19財年公司要全面擁抱智能化，在個人電腦方面要繼續保持領先的盈利能力，移動業務需積極求進，數據中心業務期望實現可持續的盈利增長，並期望在人工智能方面打造新的競爭優勢。<br />\n<br />\n他又為集團訂下五個目標，包括新型智能設備營業額達10億美元，軟件和服務總營業額達到20億美元，PC增值服務滲透率今明兩年各提升1個百分點，超大規模數據中心業務營業額達到15億美元，並冀透過利用工業IoT和大數據技術，令智能化解決方案的營業額和客戶數各增長3倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢次應該會超越大時代(2015)價位 $13.4</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f946c12637b8a41b2b57fce4fdc2976efa2c2ae0","tid":632337,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aceedf984190f5b991183dde6a9baa2d3456b0","tid":632337,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T09:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c482cee27d89398b03eb73086d8fba1f99b43f","tid":632337,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0465de7d16850ab0625718e53e530998c426188","tid":632337,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as